Class ProductionController

  • java.lang.Object
    • ProductionController
  • public class ProductionController
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Tyler Krawec

    Controller class to control my Production stage and related fxml file. Connects to my database and allows for user entered input.

      Populates the text area in my GUI with data from my ProductionRecord table.
      void populateTypeBox()
      Populates the choice box on my GUI with the possible item types from the ItemType enum
      void recordProduction()
      Selects a product from my list view and quantity from my combo box to to create production records for any product saved in the Product table and saves data to the ProductionRecord table
      void updateProduct()
      Adds user entered data to my Product table in my database
